description: Move-in ready, 2BR/2BA, nestled in the heart of S. Boston features a modern, fully equipped stainless-steel kitchen with gleaming granite countertops, a wine fridge, & abundant storage for all your culinary needs. Both full-size bathrooms are appointed with updated tile, one boasting a relaxing jacuzzi tub. Enjoy the convenience of an in-unit washer/dryer. Elegantly designed with crown molding in the bedrooms and polished hardwood floors throughout, this home is as stylish as it is functional. Step outside to your large private rear deck, ideal for unwinding or entertaining. Located just a short stroll from E & W Broadway, you'll have access to an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as the Broadway T Station, making commuting a breeze. This condo offers a lifestyle of luxury and ease!
